The Minister may, by statutory instrument, make regulations for Zambia, or any part thereof, not inconsistent with this Act, for all or any of the following purposes:
(a) prescribing the qualifications, powers and duties of inspectors and other persons designated to exercise powers and perform duties under this Act;
